sentences: Diana Reyes (born November 18, 1979) is a regional Mexican musical artist.
Reyes was born in La Paz, Baja California Sur, Mexico.
She has released three gold records since 2004:
La Reina del Pasito Duranguense, Las No. 1 de la Reina, and Te Voy a Mostrar.
Reyes holds strong ties to her father's native state of Sinaloa and her mother's native Sonora.
